Thanks to my partner @pacificobeer for putting together this piece on how I prepare for the Olympics while staying balanced and happy in my day to day life...

What’s your life philosophy for working towards goals and maintaining your overall wellbeing? 💙💙💙

#LiveLifeAnchorsUp
#For21+ 
#jafreespirit 
#jalivingthedream

node.text:
Life is meant to be lived to its fullest potential! In order to do so, I want to feel my best – Physically, mentally and spiritually! ✨ Thankful to be a part of this all natural CBD brand made right here in the USA! Take a look at the first athlete announcements with more to come soon–  Follow @justlive and visit the link in my bio 💙 @alexmorgan13 @klaythompson @prod @travispastrana @alexmidler @alecmajerus @ishodwair @mannysantiago @atibaphoto  @sagekotsenburg @johncollinson @camzink #justlive #athletefounded #naturegrounded

node.text:
“Earth provides enough to satisfy every man's needs, but not every man's greed ”. 

- Mahatma Gandhi

Visiting @fairycreekblockade last week was eye opening.... 

Thank you to everyone there helping in many different ways! I am very inspired by the community of like minded people wanting to help and protect a very special place 🙏 

For everyone who wants to help but maybe doesn’t know where to begin, remember that small changes can have a big impact! 

Simple things like supporting biodiverse farming, bamboo, hemp, small local business, being kind to those around you, recycling, growing your own food... It’s all energy and vibration and the more we choose to change our lifestyle and patterns, the more we can influence positive change and lifestyle around the world... 

All my love and prayers to everyone out there, we’re in this together 🙏
